S = \sum\limits_{i=1}^{n} i2^i
2S = \sum_{i=1}^{n}i2^{i+1}=\sum_{i=1}^{n}(i+1-1)2^{i+1} = \sum_{i=2}^{n+1}i2^{i}-\sum_{i=1}^{n}2^{i+1}= S+ (n+1)2^{n+1}-(1)2^1 -\sum_{i=1}^{n}2^{i+1}
S=(n+1)2^{n+1}-(1)2^1 -\sum_{i=1}^{n}2^{i+1}
S_n = \sum_{i=1}^n i 2^i
S_{n+1} = 2S_n + \sum_{i=1}^{n} 2^i = 2S_n + (2^{n+1} - 1)
